 Andrea Ekeng Inyang Governor, Ben Ayade’s Special Assistant on Strategic Communication, Andrea Ekeng Inyang, took to social media to share a photo of the burnt Puff Puff made by his wife. According to him, his wife watched a video on YouTube and decided to try it before it ended drastically. READ ALSO: Money Rains As Brand Influencer, Ama Reginald Shuts Down Lagos On Her 22nd Birthday Party (Video) “After my wife watched YouTube video on how to make puff puff, she made us drive to the market to buy the items. Ladies and gentlemen, this is the result. Boki puff puff on zero budget” he wrote. 